      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "# ⚡ Z-Fooocus\n",
        "**Generate · Img2Img · Inpaint** — All powered by Z-Image Turbo FP8\n",
        "\n",
        "A [Fooocus](https://github.com/lllyasviel/Fooocus)-style app for [Z-Image Turbo](https://github.com/Tongyi-MAI/Z-Image) on Free Google Colab.\n",
        "\n",
        "| Tab | What it does |\n",
        "|-----|--------------|\n",
        "| 🖼️ Generate | Text → Image |\n",
        "| ✏️ Img2Img | Upload photo + prompt → Restyled photo |\n",
        "| 🎨 Inpaint | Paint mask → Only that area gets regenerated |\n",
        "\n",
        "**Instructions:** Run Step 1 → wait for ✅ → Run Step 2 → click the Gradio link!\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "Based on [NeuralFalconYT/Z-Image-Colab](https://github.com/NeuralFalconYT/Z-Image-Colab)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "intro_md"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {
        "cellView": "form",
        "id": "install_cell"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "#@title 📦 Step 1: Install & Download (~5 min)\n",
        "\n",
        "# ── ComfyUI ────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
        "%cd /content/\n",
        "!git clone https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI\n",
        "%cd /content/ComfyUI\n",
        "\n",
        "PIN_COMMIT = \"3c8456223c5f6a41af7d99219b391c8c58acb552\"\n",
        "if PIN_COMMIT:\n",
        "    !git fetch --all -q\n",
        "    !git reset --hard {PIN_COMMIT}\n",
        "\n",
        "!pip install -r requirements.txt\n",
        "\n",
        "# ── Download app.py ────────────────────────────────────\n",
        "
        "!wget -q -O app.py https://raw.githubusercontent.com/MuntasirMalek/Z-Fooocus/main/app.py\n",
        "\n",
        "# ── Fast downloader ────────────────────────────────────\n",
        "!apt -y install -qq aria2\n",
        "\n",
        "# ── Z-Image Turbo FP8 ─────────────────────────────────\n",
        "print('\\n⬇️ Downloading Z-Image Turbo FP8...')\n",
        "!aria2c --console-log-level=error -c -x 16 -s 16 -k 1M \\\n",
        "    https://huggingface.co/T5B/Z-Image-Turbo-FP8/resolve/main/z-image-turbo-fp8-e4m3fn.safetensors \\\n",
        "    -d /content/ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models \\\n",
        "    -o z-image-turbo-fp8-e4m3fn.safetensors\n",
        "\n",
        "!aria2c --console-log-level=error -c -x 16 -s 16 -k 1M \\\n",
        "    https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_4b.safetensors \\\n",
        "    -d /content/ComfyUI/models/clip \\\n",
        "    -o qwen_3_4b.safetensors\n",
        "\n",
        "!aria2c --console-log-level=error -c -x 16 -s 16 -k 1M \\\n",
        "    https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors \\\n",
        "    -d /content/ComfyUI/models/vae \\\n",
        "    -o ae.safetensors\n",
        "\n",
        "# ── Verify ─────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
        "from IPython.display import clear_output\n",
        "clear_output()\n",
        "\n",
        "import os\n",
        "paths = [\n",
        "    '/content/ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/z-image-turbo-fp8-e4m3fn.safetensors',\n",
        "    '/content/ComfyUI/models/clip/qwen_3_4b.safetensors',\n",
        "    '/content/ComfyUI/models/vae/ae.safetensors',\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "all_ok = True\n",
        "for p in paths:\n",
        "    name = os.path.basename(p)\n",
        "    if os.path.exists(p):\n",
        "        size_gb = os.path.getsize(p) / 1e9\n",
        "        print(f'  ✅ {name} ({size_gb:.1f} GB)')\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "        print(f'  ❌ MISSING: {name}')\n",
        "        all_ok = False\n",
        "\n",
        "if all_ok:\n",
        "    print('\\n\\033[92m✅ All models ready! Run Step 2 to launch.\\033[0m')\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    print('\\n\\033[91m⚠️ Some downloads failed. Re-run this cell.\\033[0m')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Keep Alive\n",
        "from IPython.display import Audio, display\n",
        "display(Audio('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/KoboldAI/KoboldAI-Client/main/colab/silence.m4a', autoplay=True))"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "#@title 🚀 Step 2: Launch Z-Fooocus\n",
        "%cd /content/ComfyUI\n",
        "!python app.py"
      ],
